Package gitlet

package gitlet
  • Class
    Description
    Blob
    Blob class that represents a file, including the file's name, the file's contents, and the SHA-1 hash of the file.
    Branch
    Class that represents the Branch object, a single object that stores mappings of all Branch names to their respective Commit hashes.
    Commit
    This class represents a Commit, which contains information about a certain commit, including its message, timestamp, parent(s), and of course, its Blobs.
    Diff
    A comparison of two sequences of strings.
    Dumpable
    An interface describing dumpable objects.
    DumpObj
    A debugging class whose main program may be invoked as follows: java gitlet.DumpObj FILE...
    GitletException
    General exception indicating a Gitlet error.
    Main
    Driver class for Gitlet, the tiny stupid version-control system.
    Remote
    Class that represents and deals with Remote repository behavior.
    Stage
    Class that represents both the Add and Remove Stages.
    UnitTest
    The suite of all JUnit tests for the gitlet package.
    Utils
    Assorted utilities.
